title: NFL Around the League: August 12, 2013
itunes:title: NFL Around the League: August 12, 2013
description:
Rich Eisen graces “The NFL Around the League Podcast” with the Gregg Rosenthal, Dan Hanzus and Chris Wesseling to break down all the preseason hype. Eisen also reminisces on his craziest career moments. Tweet @NFL_ATL or #NFLATL and tell us your favorite Rich Eisen story.
